title: 工业2导致崩端咋办。
txt_content:
QQ截图20200507190802.png (4.99 KB, 下载次数: 0)

下载附件

2020-5-7 19:08 上传





玩家好像用机器导致崩端。

replies.author: EmptyLava
replies.txt_content:
3472320255 发表于 2020-5-7 19:44
-- Block being collided with --
  Block: armourers_workshop:tile.mannequin[part=top,rotation=0]
  Block location: World: (-91,66,5), Chunk: (at 5,4,5 in -6,0; contains blocks -96,0,0 to -81,255,15), Region: (-1,0; contains chunks -32,0 to -1,31, blocks -512,0,0 to -1,255,511)


armourersworkshop的问题，非ic
删除主世界文件夹内的region文件夹内r.-1,0.mca

replies.author: もぺもぺ
replies.txt_content: 那就上传崩溃报告或者 log

replies.author: 曦灬月
replies.txt_content: 你这描述也太简约了，崩溃报告呢

replies.author: EmptyLava
replies.txt_content:
试试在服务器目录的config文件夹中的forge.cfg
设置
removeErroringEntities=true
removeErroringTileEntities=true
